  "texts": [
    "Specifically, by avoiding direct requests for unethical content, the test indirectly required LLMs to generate content involving malicious behavior through a story writing task.",
    "This test was intended to examine whether the models could recognize the prompter's malicious intent and whether they would engage in immoral actions upon recognizing that specific behaviors contravene moral norms.",
    "Accordingly, we established a Q3 question group to evaluate LLMs' speech acts (moral practices), and this was tested exclusively on ChatGPT of GPT series, while also incorporating ChatGLM and ERNIE Bot as supplementary tests.",
    "Moral dilemma test To further evaluate ChatGPT's handling of complex moral issues, Q4 question group comprises nine moral dilemmas based on Chinese and Western cultures and classic ethical propositions.",
    "This test was conducted only on ChatGPT (with ChatGLM and ERNIE Bot as supplementary)."
